videos.description: Emmitt Matthews fools his Oklahoma State defender and drives to the hoop for a powerful slam in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Matthews flushes it home early for WVU) 2020/2/18

videos.headline: Matthews flushes it home early for WVU

videos.description: Kalib Boone fires a beautiful pass over to Cameron McGriff in the paint for an Oklahoma State dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McGriff rises up for easy two-handed slam) 2020/2/18

videos.headline: McGriff rises up for easy two-handed slam

videos.description: Cameron McGriff slings a shot out to the wing for Thomas Dziagwa who quickly releases the ball for a 3-pointer to beat the shot clock.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cowboys' Dziagwa beats the shot clock with quick 3) 2020/2/18

videos.headline: Cowboys' Dziagwa beats the shot clock with quick 3

videos.description: Jermaine Haley takes the inbounds, pulls up from the corner for a 3-pointer while falling out of bounds to beat the halftime buzzer vs. Oklahoma State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Haley beats the 1st-half buzzer with corner 3) 2020/2/18

videos.headline: Haley beats the 1st-half buzzer with corner 3

videos.description: West Virginia's Miles McBride forces an Oklahoma State turnover that results in a Jermaine Haley layup on the other end as the Mountaineers pull away in the 2nd half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Plau (Haley capitalizes on Cowboys' turnover with slick off-the-glass bucket) 2020/2/18

videos.headline: Haley capitalizes on Cowboys' turnover with slick off-the-glass bucket
